                          ssh-gnome-keyring-connection
                         ------------------------------

	ssh-gnome-keyring-connection allows the user to automatically add keys
to the ssh-agent upon logging in without to type in the passphrases. The
passphrases are stored and retrieved from the GNOME Keyring.

                                 Prerequisites
                                ---------------

The following packages are required to build ssh-gnome-keyring-connection:

libglib2.0-dev
libgnome-keyring-dev

